title: Mid-Century W. Germany Ceramic Vase
description: A patterned dark blue vase has been fitted with modern brass adjustable fixture and E26 lighting socket. These ceramic vases were produced primarily in the 1970s, marked with "W.GERMANY" stamp on bottom. High quality stoneware, with distinctive mid-century color schemes and graphic patterns and textures, this floor lamp includes a vintage patterned fabric shade.
